Package edu.cnm.deepdive.heydoc

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppointmentFragment
    This is the AppointmentFragment class that extends Fragment.
    CalendarActivity
    The CalendarActivity class extends the Activity class and sets the parameters for the calendar.
    FavoritesFragment
    The FavoritesFragment inflates the fragment_favorites layout.
    HomeFragment
    The HomeFragment class extends the Fragment class and inflates the elements of the home page including the list of scheduled appointments.
    LoginActivity
    the LoginActivity class sets the parameters for the log in page which requires a username and a password.
    MainActivity
    The MainActivity class utilizes the toolbar features and establishes a home fragment that allows the user to access the home screen from the navigation drawer.
    PractitionerListFragment
    The PractitionerListFragment creates the list of practitioners that is available to the user.
    ProfileFragment
    The ProfileFragment class has several elements to it including the calendar and the rating bar for each one of the practitioners.
    ScheduleItem
    The ScheduleItem class establishes the parameters for an appointment.
    SpecialtyFragment
    The SpecialtyFragment sets the parameters for the list of Specialists and inflates that fragment.
    TimeListAdapter
    The TimeList adapter is used primarily to change the background color of the practitioners schedule based on whether the appointment has been booked or not.
    UniDatabase
    The Database implements the series of Dao classes.
    UserStatsFragment
    The UserStatsFragment utilizes a FloatingAction Button to access its contents.
